<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">当下列条件满足时，萤火虫灌木丛有概率会发出特殊的环境音效：</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">晚上</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">上方除树叶、地毯、竹笋外无任何固体方块阻挡</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">枯叶</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶是一种能在森林、 黑森林以及疏林恶地找到的新的装饰性方块</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">注: 枯叶仅以世界生成的一部分生成，并在游戏中不会重新生成</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以在一格方块空间内有不同数量的枯叶片</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">在同一格方块空间内最多有四片</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">对已有枯叶方块放置枯叶会增加枯叶的数量</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以以四种方向放置枯叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶可以放置在有完整顶面的方块上</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶可以由任意树叶方块烧炼而成</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶可以被当作烧炼燃料</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶可以被用于堆肥</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶拥有独特的方块音效</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">枯叶会随所处的生物群系着色</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">当放置方块时枯叶可以被方块直接替换</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">野花簇</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">野花簇是一种新的花，生成于桦木森林、原始桦木森林和草甸</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以在一格方块空间内有不同数量的野花簇</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">在同一格方块空间内最多有四簇</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">对已有野花簇方块放置野花簇会增加野花簇的数量</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">对野花簇使用骨粉会生成更多野花簇</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">可以以四种方向放置野花簇</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">野花簇可以合成黄色染料</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">灌木丛</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">灌木丛是一种新的装饰方块，会在以下生物群系以斑块形式生成：</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">桦木森林</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">森林</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">冻河</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">原始桦木森林</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">平原</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">河流</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">风袭森林</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">风袭沙砾丘陵</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">风袭丘陵</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">灌木丛可以被用于堆肥</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">对其使用骨粉会在附近可生成位置生成新灌木丛</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">灌木丛仅能由剪刀或附有精准采集的工具破坏时掉落</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">当放置方块时灌木丛可以被方块直接替换</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">矮枯草丛和高枯草丛</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">增加了两种新的草：矮枯草丛和高枯草丛 </Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">都只有一格高，意味着高枯草丛与两格高的高草丛不同</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">都在沙漠与恶地生物群系生成</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">与枯萎的灌木一样能放置于沙子、陶瓦和泥土类方块上</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">对其使用骨粉</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">矮枯草丛会生长为高枯草丛</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">高枯草丛在其周围的有效位置生成矮枯草丛</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">均可用于堆肥</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">绵羊可以食用它们重新长出羊毛</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">都可用于作为烧炼燃料</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">当放置方块时都可被方块直接替换</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">仙人掌花</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">仙人掌花是一种新的花，有概率生成在沙漠和恶地的仙人掌上</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">仙人掌花可以被放置在仙人掌、耕地或任何顶部提供中心支持的方块上</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">仙人掌花有概率生成在仙人掌上，并阻止仙人掌长得更高</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">如果仙人掌 1-2 格高，仙人掌花则有 10% 的概率生长</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">如果仙人掌 3 格高，仙人掌花则有 25% 的概率生长</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">仙人掌花仅当四面均无固体方块时才会生长</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">仙人掌花可以被用于堆肥</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">仙人掌花可以合成一个粉色染料</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">落叶粒子</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">所有树叶方块有概率生成落叶粒子</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">下列方块受本次更改影响： </Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">金合欢树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">杜鹃树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">白桦树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">深色橡树树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">盛开的杜鹃树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">丛林树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">红树树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">橡树树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">云杉树叶</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">沙漠和恶地的新环境音效</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">当玩家周围被至少 3 个方向，最小 8 格远的沙子、红沙或任意颜色的陶瓦包围，有一定几率播放环境音效</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">block.sand.idle</TextBox> 在任意生物群系均可播放</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">block.sand.wind</TextBox> 仅在沙漠和恶地群系播放</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">当枯萎的灌木丛在任意生物群系，两个任意颜色的陶瓦、沙子或红沙上方时有一定几率播放环境音效</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
